    <title>Site Metrics Report</title>
    <shortdesc>
      <wintitle>Site Metrics</wintitle> reports display quantitative
		information about your website. For example, they show how many times visitors
		looked at pages, the numbers of purchases made from specific pages, the time
		spent on pages, revenue, and similar quantitative data. Each of these reports
		is a metric that you can place in other item-based reports. 
	 </shortdesc>
    <prolog>
